text: José Defran (born 1 January 1938) is a Dominican Republic wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 52 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Dominican Republic male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Dominican Republic Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from La Vega Province
